    <h2>MISSIONS</h2>
    <p>Lighting &amp; Thunder Ministry have a vision for seeing the Kingdom of God advanced on the earth by setting the captives free and living in the light of God’s Word.  Our heart for the mission field as is to see the lost saved, healed and delivered through the power of the Holy Spirit. When we go into a foreign nation, we go in with the power of the Gospel, speaking prophetic decrees that break curses and cultural strongholds over regions.</p>

<div class=verse><p>Go into all the world and preach the gospel to every creature. - Mark 16:15</p></div>



